  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="white_box_shadow"><a name="top"></a>
<p><span class="geolocation-title"><img src="/media/13049120/ski-hire-big.jpg" alt="Ski hire on your Inghams ski holiday" data-udi="umb://media/003eace1afe6498da6b1b3e309310e0c" /></span></p>
<p><span class="geolocation-title">Getting all your ski equipment sorted for your ski holiday can be a daunting prospect. Fortunately, by pre-booking your equipment with Inghams, our in resort representatives will organise everything in advance for you, have your vouchers ready on arrival, and guide you towards your hire shop. Travel to the slopes with ease this winter and pre-book your ski hire with Inghams.</span></p>
<p><strong><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/ski-holiday-essentials/ski-hire#01">Ski hire categories</a></strong></p>
<p><strong><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/ski-holiday-essentials/ski-hire#03">How to pre-book your ski hire</a></strong></p>
<p><strong><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/ski-holiday-essentials/ski-hire#04">Exchanging skis and snowboards</a></strong></p>
<p><strong><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/ski-holiday-essentials/ski-hire#05">Hiring helmets</a></strong></p>
<div class="data-grid" style="float: center;">
<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" class="tablet-button" style="height: 20px; width: 300px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
<tbody>
